{
  "texts": [
    "Although not extensively, ML algorithms have been utilized in the gamification process to improve some individual components of the game.",
    "In one example, a game called \"NTU Social Game\" has been formulated around reductions in energy in a residential dormitory.",
    "Here, players compete against each other to have the lowest energy, and accrue points depending on how much less energy they consume.",
    "Prizes are not simply doled out according to whoever has the highest energy reductions; instead, players are entered into a prize pool if they are among the top third performing participants.",
    "A small number of prizes are allocated randomly among the winning pool as per the Vickrey Clarke Groves (VCG) auction mechanism."
  ]
}